snippet.title: (Reupload) Mushroom Kingdom Fusion NCFC '08 Trailer #2
snippet.description:
This is the second trailer for Mushroom Kingdom Fusion for the 2008 Nintendo Community Fangame Convention (NCFC). It showcases most of the major features of the game, as well as showcasing previews of the many different enemies, levels, and bosses.

Originally uploaded to IndieDB on October 22, 2008.
